<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">To shorten it up to not give too much away, it is coming to terms with life. Sometimes life is beautiful and forgiving. Other times life is cruel and <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">â¦more</a></span><span class="fullContent">To shorten it up to not give too much away, it is coming to terms with life. Sometimes life is beautiful and forgiving. Other times life is cruel and unkind. It's about learning to let go and move on to who you are going to be.<br />This is kind of a vague answer, but how I felt at a basic level.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
