              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13643260749964630759">Don&apos;t be fooled by the cover or the title. <br/>The book is okay written, but the most beautifully written part is the last few pages, when Zoe finally understand how to let go of someone you love with the help of Simon. Simon, the lone vampire, is in turn, helped by Zoe herself, who shows him how it is to be noticed and be loved. A very great book...nearly cried reading the last parts. </span>
  <span id="freeText13643260749964630759" style="display:none">Don't be fooled by the cover or the title. <br />The book is okay written, but the most beautifully written part is the last few pages, when Zoe finally understand how to let go of someone you love with the help of Simon. Simon, the lone vampire, is in turn, helped by Zoe herself, who shows him how it is to be noticed and be loved. A very great book...nearly cried reading the last parts. </span>
